        "content": "Dr. Schmidt, I've drafted my proposal for a universal traffic prediction system. I want to build a GCN that can be trained on OSM road graphs from any city and generalize across layouts. f1.pdf is the first version."
      },
      {
        "type": "file",
        "time": "2026-03-25T10:01:00+08:00",
